  verdict: "<strong>The defining Bay Street restaurant.</strong> Open seasonally roughly April through Columbus Day. Reservations are taken and recommended on summer weekends — older guides that say \"no reservations\" are out of date. Hours: 4–10 PM Monday through Wednesday; 12–10 PM Thursday through Sunday. Phone: <strong>(401) 348-8211</strong>.",
